"22:5:64" : {s: 22, a: 5, w: 64, r: "ربو", t: "وَرَبَتْ", l: "رَبَتْ", lc: 4, tl: "warabat", lb: "বৃদ্ধি পাওয়া",e: "and it swells", b: "", i: "dan suburlah ia", f: 2, rm: "it increased/augmented, the practicing/taking of usury, excess/addition, an addition obtained more than what is supposed to be received, become high/grown up/large/swollen/risen, mount up, to grow/swell, out of breath, panting. rabiyatun - ever-increasing, severe. arba (comp. form) - more numerous, more increased."},
